Cell - Class in api
Data type for one cell in a Minesweeper game.
Cell(int, int) - Constructor for class api.Cell
Constructs a cell to be located at the given row and column.
CELL_SIZE - Static variable in class ui.MinesweeperPanel
Size in pixels of the cells for the grid.
CellObserver - Interface in api
Interface representing a component that may be notified when a cell's status changes.
clearRegion(Cell[][], int, int, ArrayList<Cell>) - Static method in class hw2.GridUtil
Performs a "flood fill" algorithm to reveal a region of all reachable cells with count zero, plus the cells at the boundary of the region, starting at the given position.
convertToStringArray(Cell[][], boolean) - Static method in class hw2.GridUtil
Converts a grid into an array of strings.
countAllFlags(Cell[][]) - Static method in class hw2.GridUtil
Returns the total number of cells marked as FLAG in the given array.
countAllMines(Cell[][]) - Static method in class hw2.GridUtil
Returns the total number of mines in the given array.
countNeighboringMines(Cell[][], int, int) - Static method in class hw2.GridUtil
Counts the number of neighbors of the given position (left, right, top, bottom, and diagonal) that are mines.
createFromStringArray(String[]) - Static method in class hw2.GridUtil
Creates a 2D array of Cells from an array of strings, where each string corresponds to one row of the returned array.
